          "%md ",
          "Next let's use **Grouping and Aggregation** to find out how many Vertices and Edges there for each Label. We use two other common SQL constructs here GROUP BY and COUNT.",
          "",
          "### Query 3: Count of Vertices by Label",
          "SELECT LABEL(v) as Vertex_Label, COUNT(v) as Number_of_Vertices FROM MATCH (v) ON SH_PGVIEW_GRAPH GROUP BY Vertex_Label",
          "",
          "### Query 4: Count of Edges by Label ",
          "SELECT LABEL(e) as Edge_Label, COUNT(e) as Number_of_Edges FROM MATCH ()-[e]->() ON SH_PGVIEW_GRAPH GROUP BY Edge_Label"
        ],
        "selectedVisualization" : "html",
        "visualizationConfig" : null,
        "hideCode" : false,
        "hideResult" : false,
        "hideGutter" : true,
