          "interpreter" : "md",
          "taskStatus" : "SUCCESS",
          "status" : "SUCCESS",
          "results" : [
            {
              "message" : "<p>Next let's use <strong>Grouping and Aggregation</strong> to find out how many Vertices and Edges there for each Label. We use two other common SQL constructs here GROUP BY and COUNT.</p>\n<h3 id=\"query-3-count-of-vertices-by-label\">Query 3: Count of Vertices by Label</h3>\n<p>SELECT LABEL(v) as Vertex_Label, COUNT(v) as Number_of_Vertices FROM MATCH (v) ON SH_PGVIEW_GRAPH GROUP BY Vertex_Label</p>\n<h3 id=\"query-4-count-of-edges-by-label\">Query 4: Count of Edges by Label</h3>\n<p>SELECT LABEL(e) as Edge_Label, COUNT(e) as Number_of_Edges FROM MATCH ()-[e]-&gt;() ON SH_PGVIEW_GRAPH GROUP BY Edge_Label</p>\n",
              "type" : "HTML"
            }
          ],
          "forms" : null
