          "%md",
          "#### Sorting and limiting the result size",
          "Sorting is done with ORDER BY (ascending or descending). While LIMIT and optionally OFFSET determine the result size and set.  ",
          "LIMIT n limits the result to the first n rows. OFFSET m starts counting the n (for LIMIT n) from rown m. LIMIT 10 OFFSET 5 will return rows 6 through 15. ",
          "",
          "#### Query 8: List top 10 sales in terms of AMOUNT_SOLD for 1998",
          "",
          "`SELECT c.CUST_FIRST_NAME, s.AMOUNT_SOLD FROM MATCH (s:SALES)->(c:CUSTOMERS) ON SH_PGVIEW_GRAPH ORDER BY s.AMOUNT_SOLD DESC LIMIT 10`",
          "",
          "#### Query 9: List the next top 10 (i.e. 11 through 20) sales in terms of AMOUNT_SOLD for 1998",
          "`SELECT c.CUST_FIRST_NAME, s.AMOUNT_SOLD FROM MATCH (s:SALES)->(c:CUSTOMERS) ON SH_PGVIEW_GRAPH ORDER BY s.AMOUNT_SOLD DESC LIMIT 10 OFFSET 10`"
        ],
        "selectedVisualization" : "html",
        "visualizationConfig" : null,
