          "status" : "SUCCESS",
          "results" : [
            {
              "message" : "<h4 id=\"sorting-and-limiting-the-result-size\">Sorting and limiting the result size</h4>\n<p>Sorting is done with ORDER BY (ascending or descending). While LIMIT and optionally OFFSET determine the result size and set.<br />\nLIMIT n limits the result to the first n rows. OFFSET m starts counting the n (for LIMIT n) from rown m. LIMIT 10 OFFSET 5 will return rows 6 through 15.</p>\n<h4 id=\"query-8-list-top-10-sales-in-terms-of-amount_sold-for-1998\">Query 8: List top 10 sales in terms of AMOUNT_SOLD for 1998</h4>\n<p><code>SELECT c.CUST_FIRST_NAME, s.AMOUNT_SOLD FROM MATCH (s:SALES)-&gt;(c:CUSTOMERS) ON SH_PGVIEW_GRAPH ORDER BY s.AMOUNT_SOLD DESC LIMIT 10</code></p>\n<h4 id=\"query-9-list-the-next-top-10-ie-11-through-20-sales-in-terms-of-amount_sold-for-1998\">Query 9: List the next top 10 (i.e. 11 through 20) sales in terms of AMOUNT_SOLD for 1998</h4>\n<p><code>SELECT c.CUST_FIRST_NAME, s.AMOUNT_SOLD FROM MATCH (s:SALES)-&gt;(c:CUSTOMERS) ON SH_PGVIEW_GRAPH ORDER BY s.AMOUNT_SOLD DESC LIMIT 10 OFFSET 10</code></p>\n",
              "type" : "HTML"
            }
          ],
