          "An EXISTS clause returns TRUE if the subquery has a result and FALSE otherwise.   ",
          "",
          "We use it in the next query to test that there is no path from Cust #1840 to a particular product P. Which means cust 1840 did not purchase that product.",
          "",
          "The query lists 10 customers in NL who purchased products that cust #1840 did not purchase ordered by the number of products they do not have in common."
        ],
