          "results" : [
            {
              "message" : "<h3 id=\"subquery-with-exists\">Subquery with <code>EXISTS</code>.</h3>\n<p>An EXISTS clause returns TRUE if the subquery has a result and FALSE otherwise.</p>\n<p>We use it in the next query to test that there is no path from Cust #1840 to a particular product P. Which means cust 1840 did not purchase that product.</p>\n<p>The query lists 10 customers in NL who purchased products that cust #1840 did not purchase ordered by the number of products they do not have in common.</p>\n",
              "type" : "HTML"
