              "message" : "<h3 id=\"path-finding-examples\">Path finding examples</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Reachability: Is there a path from vertex A to B?</li>\n<li>Shortest: What is a shortest path from vertex A to B?</li>\n</ul>\n",
